%H A397158 <a href="/index/Al#algebraic_04">Index entries for algebraic numbers, degree 4</a>.
%F A397158 Equals sqrt(9/28 + 13/(28*sqrt(2))) = sqrt(9/28 + 13/(28*A002193)).
%F A397158 Equals the largest real root of 224*x^4 - 144*x^2 - 1.
%e A397158 0.8060571619978572723377430748752989068396335482017...
%t A397158 First[RealDigits[Sqrt[9/28 + 13/(28*Sqrt[2])], 10, 100]]
%t A397158 (* Alternative: *)
%t A397158 First[RealDigits[PolyhedronData[{"Trapezohedron", 4}, "Inradius"], 10, 100]]
